89,"payout_ratio":0.0,"revenue":1929927040.0,"revenue_per_share":96.596,"revenue_growth":-0.318,"ebitda":103109504.0,"ebitda_margins":0.05343,"gross_margins":0.30078,"operating_margins":0.059720002,"profit_margins":0.019550001,"net_income":37732000.0,"total_cash":513000.0,"total_cash_per_share":0.026,"total_debt":316060992.0,"debt_to_equity":32.821,"current_ratio":1.932,"return_on_equity":0.040430002,"enterprise_value":1197186688.0,"enterprise_to_ebitda":11.611,"enterprise_to_revenue":0.62,"earnings_growth":-0.37,"shares_outstanding":19921783.0,"float_shares":4323631.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.91168,"held_pct_institutions":0.0,"beta":-0.459,"fifty_two_week_high":78.5,"fifty_two_week_low":43.0,"fifty_day_average":54.567,"two_hundred_day_avg":60.9975,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":85.0,"all_time_low":45.0,"long_business_summary":"Rungta Irrigation Limited engages in the design, manufacture, assemble, and market of pipe-based sprinkler irrigation systems in India and internationally. The company offers casing pipes; MDPE pipes; rigid, elastomeric, and self-fit PVC pipes; high density polyethylene (HDPE) pipes; sprinkler irrigation and drip irrigation systems; ball valves; and others. It also provides micro irrigation systems, such as online drip, inline drip, mini sprinkler, rainguns, portable sprinkler sets, and UGPL systems. In addition, the company offers rotating sprinklers; winkler, mikro, butterfly, superfly, screen, and disc products; automatic filters; flush, pressure release, solenoid, and control valves; pressure gauges; air vents; drip fittings; irrigation controllers, and other irrigation products. Further, it undertakes EPC contracts that covers engineering design, procurement, and supply of materials. The company serves agriculture, horticulture, tea, coffee, rubber, and cardamom plantation sectors. Rungta Irrigation Limited was incorporated in 1986 and is headquartered in New Delhi, India."}}